---
import Container from "@/components/common/Container.astro";
import Button from "@/components/common/Button.astro";
---

<section class="relative pt-20 pb-32 md:pt-32 md:pb-48 overflow-hidden">
  <Container>
    <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-8">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-text-primary">
          Data Engineer <br />
          <span class="text-text-muted font-semibold text-2xl sm:text-4xl mt-2 block">
            Architecting Reliable, Scalable Data Pipelines.
          </span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-muted max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
          Fokus pada pengolahan data dalam skala besar dengan performa tinggi.
          Mengembangkan pipeline yang tahan banting, mudah di-maintain, dan siap distribusi.
          Mengutamakan kualitas data, efisiensi storage, dan desain arsitektur yang future-proof.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <Button href="#contact" size="lg">
          Contact Me
        </Button>
        <Button href="/cv.pdf" variant="outline" size="lg">
          Download CV
        </Button>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-8 border-t border-border grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-12 w-fit">
        <div>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary">2+</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider">Years Exp.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-text-primary">20+</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-wider">Projects</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>